title: The Sound View. Northwest Corner 140th Street and Convent Avenue.

text:
College of the City of New York: The Main Building on St. Nicholas Terrace, seen from St. Nicholas Park. On the right is the Chemistry Building, at the S. W. corner of Convent Avenue and W. 140th Street, across the roof of which appears the chimney of the Technology Building.

About 1915

Gift of Urbrock Collection
title: Colleges and Universities - College of the City of New York - [City University of New York.]

text:
College of the City of New York:

Main Building of the College of the City of New York, Convent Avenue, from but not including 136th, to but not including 140th Streets.

About 1925.

Ewing Galloway.
